headline: Striking Canada Post workers ‘endanger’ future parcel business, execs say

headline: Swiftair, European Leader in Outsourced Express Airfreight, Welcomes Antin to Accelerate Its Growth
summary: PARIS & LONDON & NEW YORK, October 01, 2025--Regulatory News: Antin Infrastructure Partners (Paris:ANTIN) is acquiring a majority stake in Swiftair Group to support a new phase of growth at the leading European provider of aircraft leasing and air transportation solutions for time-critical cargo.
